"{\"uid\": \"siasat.com-japanese-olympic-champ-higuchi-consoles-vinesh-says-i-understand-your-pain-3076995\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Paris:All too familiar with the pain of being disqualified over a few extra grams, Japanese Olympic champion Rei Higuchi offered his support to Indian wrestler Vinesh Phogat, who was debarred from her final in the Paris Games for being 100gm above the prescribed limit.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9508749492438594, \"rank\": 0.03287803883346827, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rei Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}, {\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999069501988989, \"rank\": 7.571868256425292e-05, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Higuchi, the gold-medallist in men's 57kg freestyle event, was eliminated from the qualifiers of the Tokyo Olympics three years ago for being overweight by just 50gm.\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He eventually even lost a playoff bout and could not compete in his home Olympics despite being highly rated even at that time.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I understand your pain the best.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Same 50g.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not worry about the voices around you.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Life goes on.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rising from setbacks is the most beautiful thing.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a good rest,\\\" Higuchi, who defeated India's Aman Sehrawat in the 57kg freestyle category semifinals en route his gold, wrote on X while commenting on Vinesh's retirement announcement.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9552246948460269, \"rank\": 0.030890466759352184, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valinor\", \"score\": 0.999965577449236, \"rank\": 2.8801050068591614e-05, \"text\": \"Aman\", \"types\": 